        public static boolean addToList​(Appointment appointment)
        Takes an appointment object as an input and adds it to the appointmentList. This is required to keep the object persistent and to use the object with methods that utilize the Observablelist.
        Parameters:
        appointment - The appointment object to be added to the list.
        Returns:
        true if the appointment object was added, false if not.
